# Test API endpoints

@host = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@api_key = changeme

### Health - проверка доступности
GET {{host}}/health
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Accept: application/json

### Buildings - список зданий
GET {{host}}/buildings
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Accept: application/json

### Organization by id - информация об организации
GET {{host}}/organizations/1
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Accept: application/json

### Organizations by building - организации в здании
GET {{host}}/organizations/by-building/1
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Accept: application/json

### Organizations by activity id -  организации по виду деятельности
GET {{host}}/organizations/by-activity/3
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Accept: application/json

### Organizations by activity tree - организации по дереву деятельности
GET {{host}}/organizations/by-activity-tree/1
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Accept: application/json

### Organizations by activity name (url-encoded) - поиск по названию деятельности
GET {{host}}/organizations/by-activity-name?name=Мясная продукция&include_children=true
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Accept: application/json

### Organizations search by name - поиск организаций по названию
GET {{host}}/organizations/search?name=Мясной Дом
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Accept: application/json

### Organizations near a point - организации в радиусе
GET {{host}}/organizations/near?lat=55.76&lon=37.63&radius_km=10
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Accept: application/json

### Organizations within a rectangle - организации в прямоугольной области
GET {{host}}/organizations/within-rect?min_lat=55.7&max_lat=55.8&min_lon=37.5&max_lon=37.7
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Accept: application/json
